    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a set of criteria by which a DSA implementation may be judged.  Particular issues covered include conformance to standards; performance; demonstrated interoperability.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
